I created a folder on which I wrote,

01:18:07.000 --> 01:18:13.000
Chef, any questions that arose with me to my boss,

01:18:13.000 --> 01:18:22.000
I always recorded on paper, and this sheet of paper was safely put in this folder and forgot about it.

01:18:22.000 --> 01:18:27.000
If I had any non-urgent documents requiring his signature,

01:18:27.000 --> 01:18:34.000
I grouped these documents, wrote a kind of accompanying document,

01:18:34.000 --> 01:18:39.000
and also put them in the folder.

01:18:39.000 --> 01:18:43.000
So let's see what we got as a result.

01:18:43.000 --> 01:18:49.000
The first line, the context, when will I be able to talk to the director.

01:18:49.000 --> 01:18:51.000
The associated tasks.

01:18:51.000 --> 01:18:54.000
I need to get a signature on the documents,

01:18:54.000 --> 01:18:57.000
I need to agree on the information in the catalog,

01:18:57.000 --> 01:19:02.000
and finally, I need to approve the conference program.

01:19:02.000 --> 01:19:06.000
How is the context planning organized?

01:19:06.000 --> 01:19:10.000
A checklist of questions in the folder.

01:19:10.000 --> 01:19:16.000
Pay attention to what is indicated in the brackets with the solution options.

01:19:16.000 --> 01:19:20.000
We practice not open questions to the management,

01:19:20.000 --> 01:19:25.000
