01:24:43.000 --> 01:24:46.000
We have the largest business representatives here,

01:24:46.000 --> 01:24:48.000
officials are here,

01:24:48.000 --> 01:24:57.000
and it is very convenient for us to arrange some kind of express negotiations here on the topic we need.

01:24:57.000 --> 01:24:59.000
But we forgot about this task.

01:24:59.000 --> 01:25:01.000
It is not in front of our eyes,

01:25:01.000 --> 01:25:06.000
it is planned for some long period of time,

01:25:06.000 --> 01:25:13.000
and we just do not use a very successful opportunity to solve this task right now.

01:25:13.000 --> 01:25:17.000
In this case, we do not forget about anything,

01:25:17.000 --> 01:25:25.000
because we monitor our annual tasks once a week.

01:25:25.000 --> 01:25:30.000
In addition, we do not need intermediate information carriers.

01:25:30.000 --> 01:25:35.000
Our plan for the month, our plan for the quarter, our plan for the half-year,

01:25:35.000 --> 01:25:42.000
because all these tasks are concentrated in our annual information carrier.

01:25:42.000 --> 01:25:50.000
Next, please look, once a day we monitor the task list for a week.

01:25:50.000 --> 01:25:55.000
What we have matured to be performed the next day,

01:25:55.000 --> 01:26:00.000
we move to the task list for the day.

01:26:02.000 --> 01:26:07.000
Thus, again, we do not forget anything,

01:26:07.000 --> 01:26:16.000
and at the same time we adapt quite flexibly to the circumstances that are created around us.

01:26:16.000 --> 01:26:20.000
Thus, we manage the circumstances,

01:26:20.000 --> 01:26:30.000
and we manage our own planning, planning and organization of our time in these proposed circumstances.

