01:47:18.000 --> 01:47:21.000
a certain time resource.

01:47:21.000 --> 01:47:23.000
And these tasks,

01:47:23.000 --> 01:47:27.000
because they require a certain resource of time,

01:47:27.000 --> 01:47:31.000
it is desirable to place them in the clock grid.

01:47:31.000 --> 01:47:36.000
Not, so to speak, fixing their beginning,

01:47:36.000 --> 01:47:40.000
not necessarily hard determining

01:47:40.000 --> 01:47:44.000
that, let's say, we will start writing this report at 12.

01:47:44.000 --> 01:47:45.000
No.

01:47:45.000 --> 01:47:48.000
But having allocated the necessary and sufficient

01:47:48.000 --> 01:47:51.000
time resource on the clock grid

01:47:51.000 --> 01:47:54.000
and freeing their own time

01:47:54.000 --> 01:47:59.000
from other affairs at this time.

01:47:59.000 --> 01:48:04.000
So, now we will deal with

